HOSTGATOR  Trademark Information
 HostGator.com, LLC
Design, creation, hosting, maintenance of websites for others; Hosting of digital content on the Internet; Hosting the web sites of others on a computer server for a global computer network




Perfect for these industries

Computer & Software Services & Scientific Services





Words that describe this mark
design      creation      hosting      maintenance   websites   hosting   digital   content   internet   hosting   web   sites   server   global   network    
                                    




This is a brand page for the HOSTGATOR trademark by HostGator.com, LLC 
                                in Burlington, MA, 01803.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this HOSTGATOR trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner HostGator.com, LLC of the HOSTGATOR trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the HOSTGATOR trademark.
                           






On Tuesday, March 07, 2006,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        HOSTGATOR by 
                        HostGator.com, LLC, Burlington, MA  01803.
                        The USPTO has given the HOSTGATOR 
                        trademark serial  number of  78831596.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED AND RENEWED.
                        The correspondent listed for HOSTGATOR is 
                        
                        
                                            Robert J. English of 
                                            Cowan, Liebowitz & Latman, P.C.,  114 West 47th Street, New York, NY 10036 
                                .
                            The HOSTGATOR trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Computer & Software Services & Scientific Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for HOSTGATOR 
                            is Design, creation, hosting, maintenance of websites for others; Hosting of digital content on the Internet; Hosting the web sites of others on a computer server for a global computer network. 
                            





