HostGator.com, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 29, 2017 12:33 AM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of HostGator.com, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
HostGator.com, LLC provides Web hosting services to clients, including beginners and professionals in the United States and internationally. It offers shared, reseller, VPS, and server packages. The company provides application hosting, domain names, and Windows hosting services. HostGator.com, LLC was founded in 2002 and is based in Houston, Texas. As of July 15, 2012, HostGator.com, LLC operates as a subsidiary of The Endurance International Group, Inc.


11251 Northwest FreewaySuite 400Houston, TX 77092United StatesFounded in 2002



Phone: 713-574-5287

Fax: 281-476-7800

www.hostgator.com







